OL,3,CThousands to attempt world record
OL,4,CPilates class in birthplace
OL,6,FThe birthplace of pilates is aiming to
OL,7,Fbreak the world record for the largest
OL,8,Fclass in a "global Pilates homecoming"
OL,9,Flandmark festival.
OL,11,FThousands of people are expected to
OL,12,Fgather at Knockaloe, near Peel, Isle
OL,13,Fof Man on 19 July for an official
OL,14,Fworld record attempt in the place
OL,15,Fwhere it was invented.
OL,17,FDuring the First World War, Joseph
OL,18,FPilates was brought to Knockaloe Camp,
OL,19,Fthe largest internment camp, where he
OL,20,Fbegan developing the foundations of
OL,21,Fhis exercise system.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
