PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784301515
OL,3,CThousands to attempt world record
OL,4,CPilates class in birthplace
OL,6,FHe created a series of controlled
OL,7,Fexercises that he shared with fellow
OL,8,Fdetainees that would later become the
OL,9,FPilates method.
OL,11,FLocked inside a prison, his
OL,12,Finspiration came from the island's
OL,13,Ffamous feline - the Manx cat.
OL,15,FThe event will be a global homecoming
OL,16,Ffor the international Pilates
OL,17,Fcommunity while aiming to beat the
OL,18,Fcurrent world record of 3,486
OL,19,Fparticipants in Turkey.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
