OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784301515
OL,3,CThousands to attempt world record
OL,4,CPilates class in birthplace
OL,6,FOne of the organisers, Joanna
OL,7,FCrookall, said: "As we mark 80 years
OL,8,Fof Ramsey Crookall on the Isle of Man,
OL,9,Fwe're delighted to be organising this
OL,10,Fevent on the Island.
OL,12,F"Bringing a global wellness community
OL,13,Ftogether at Knockaloe, a place of such
OL,14,Fhistorical significance, feels both
OL,15,Fmeaningful and inspiring.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
