PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1784301515
OL,3,CThousands to attempt world record
OL,4,CPilates class in birthplace
OL,6,FShe added: "As a Manx family business,
OL,7,Fsupporting initiatives that promote
OL,8,Fwellbeing, connection and positive
OL,9,Fexperiences on the Island is something
OL,10,Fwe genuinely care about, and this
OL,11,Fevent reflects that commitment."
OL,13,FFellow organiser, Stephen Baum, added:
OL,14,F"This weekend we have the chance to
OL,15,Fwrite and make history. This will be
OL,16,Fsomething truly unique and special on
OL,17,Fthe global stage."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
