OL,3,CThousands to attempt world record
OL,4,CPilates class in birthplace
OL,6,FCEO of Visit Isle of Man, Deborah
OL,7,FHeather said: "We are incredibly proud
OL,8,Fto support this landmark event, which
OL,9,Fbeautifully reflects what makes the
OL,10,FIsle of Man such an extraordinary
OL,11,Fplace to visit.
OL,13,F"To welcome a global Pilates
OL,14,Fhomecoming to the very place where it
OL,15,Fwas first conceived is both deeply
OL,16,Fsymbolic and wonderfully inspiring.
OL,18,F"It aligns perfectly with our long-
OL,19,Fterm vision to grow a visitor economy
OL,20,Frooted in authenticity, wellbeing, and
OL,21,Four UNESCO Biosphere values.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
